<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ش ر ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٨٠٦ - ش ر ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شرُفَ يَشرُف، شَرَفًا وشرافةً، فهو شَريف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شرُف الشّخصُ:</span> علت منزلتُه، سما قدرُه <span class="c1">"شرُف بآبائه- أصل شريف"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شرُف المكانُ:</span> ارتفع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>